    Taglet to provide POM coordinates as a <dependency/> element to include this documented Class or Package.

    For example:

    <dependency>
  <groupId>dev.hcf.ball</groupId>
  <artifactId>ball-tools-javadoc</artifactId>
  <version>3.1.5.20221214</version>
</dependency>
